# 🏥 Healthcare Waitlist Analysis Dashboard

## 📌 Overview

This dashboard provides an interactive view of healthcare waiting lists across different patient categories, age groups, and specialties. It enables users to monitor historical trends, identify bottlenecks, and support data-driven decision-making.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX
- Data Modeling

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

- KPI Cards
- Latest Month Waitlist
- Total Cases
- Median Wait Time
- Interactive Filters
- Specialty Analysis
- Case Type Analysis
- Age Profile
- Time Band Analysis
- Archive Date Analysis

---

## 📈 Visualizations

- Waitlist Distribution
- Waitlist by Time Band
- Historical Waitlist Trend
- Waitlist by Age Group
- Waitlist by Specialty
- Monthly Performance Analysis

---

## 🔑 Key Insights

- More than 67% of patients were on the latest monthly waiting list.
- Outpatient services recorded the highest waiting volume.
- Several specialties experienced significantly longer waiting times than others.
- Historical trends reveal periods of increasing patient backlog.

---

## 💡 Recommendations

- Allocate additional resources to high-demand specialties.
- Monitor monthly trends to reduce patient backlog.
- Optimize scheduling for outpatient services.
- Use dashboard filters to identify priority c

## 🚀 Project Outcome

This project demonstrates how Power BI can transform raw healthcare data into meaningful insights, enabling stakeholders to make informed decisions and improve patient service delivery.

